casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Carmona, Appellant, v. Pietrykowski, Clerk of Courts, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. Carmona v. Pietrykowski (1994), 69 Ohio St.3d 483.]

(No. 92-716 Submitted May 10, 1994 Decided June 22, 1994.) Jose Carmona pro se. Anthony G. Pizza Lucas County Prosecuting Attorney, and Jeffery B. Johnston, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed.

Moyer, C. J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer,, JJ., concur. Resnick, J., not participating.
